Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡无奇的日常 是无可替的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:23.81,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}这份思念之情 现在终于意识到了
