Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.94,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,834)\pos(942,0)}第九话 人生即是求生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 没有 没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经找了10天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:21.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是既没有找到球 也没有斑鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚来就把任务给办砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:56.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为到了这边 能跟雏还有杏子见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就会变成这样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子跟雏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果只是摆着的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:38.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:42.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点像了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:50.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,任务也失败了 我都不知道今后该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 说到底把你送到这种无人岛上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,斑鸠这家伙也太废物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不知道她是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:00.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她老是使唤我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里悠闲生活不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她真是个笨蛋 笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 就在这儿住段时间也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:13.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊 老是饭啊饭的 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子你才烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟裙子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 挺合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:36.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都是因为你们两个不爱打扮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪 你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说到度假就是小木屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:58.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:04:59.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你就吃果冻不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经吃烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我就来做午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给你 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:12.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说雏 你也得让我吃一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急嘛 杏子也有份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是你硬要给我 我才吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给你 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近怎么了 真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得你没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说是度假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这只不过是孤岛求生罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:49.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 这是个能好好休息的时间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对啊 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:56.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我一直一个人在这里 之后该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪我不是一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:19.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 不是杏子跟雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:25.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是两只椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:29.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,饭……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人类
