Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:57.95,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)\fs100\shad0\blur5\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1476.667,728)}超能力女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:58.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 我听说内藤大哥很恐怖的 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经是他的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他这一次进监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为他一个人拿着日本刀 反杀了对面四个带枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人称现实版刽子手内藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我头上这个伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:19.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我当年忘记帮他点烟 他用烟灰缸给砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭这些就能拍黑帮片了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对别惹他生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见啊 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们去看看老爹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:46.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经意识不清了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该听说老爹要隐退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:09:00.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却在指定接班人之前突然就昏迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么了 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说怎么有点臭 他就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你把老年臭说得委婉一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:13.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是雏把老爹弄得意识不清的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显 我会是接班人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我接管之前 还得先统一组内力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:24.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来 我好像还让你去当打手做了不少乱来的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:27.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是好像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:33.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我这也是为你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算得上是我想磨练你的一片心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说得就好像自己已经当上了组长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿 统一组织的事情就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:51.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让头儿当上组长 我会全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:53.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你已经脱胎换骨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我开心不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我首先就得跟内藤大哥商量下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是把他拿下 组里就会统一了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:11.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 大哥你也会支持头儿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我为咱们组进了监狱 出来之后还不让我往上爬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么混吃等死 让人无法接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 你应该会支持我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能先放下手里的烟灰缸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们现在说的不是烟灰缸的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很理解大哥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但能不能先忍一忍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:50.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能让组里乱起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在老头子不知道的情况下搞得组织四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就无法面对老头子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:56.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大哥为了让老爹安心 就支持头儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:10.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像是个小鬼一样 总是随着性子来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:10.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 你也算得上是一个合格的黑道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:18.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的义气超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人夸人也太不会夸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:29.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟那边来联系了 说老爹好像是醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹 我想跟你说一下你的接班人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这事说一半我就晕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,得趁我还好好的就得隐退了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那您的接班人 就定为头儿可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接班人是什么 是鱿鱼干之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你说了少说废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹一副孙女来看他了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我来撤回之前说你臭的发言了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 我喷了除味剂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:00.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,选接班人的意思就是选出下一任老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我就会变成普通的老头子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那下一任让新田来当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:15.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为新田是爸爸 又多个老爹不好区分嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:16.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆合在一起算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:21.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让新田来当老爹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是她爷爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别一副「给你糖糖吃」的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧跟下边说一下
