Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(746.667,434.667)\frz22.47}你之后去医院看看老爹的状况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz23.78\3c&H30593B&\c&H325540&\pos(1341.333,402.667)}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz20.24\pos(1090.667,650.666)}头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz22.93\pos(1354.667,544.001)}老爹他醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.36,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz24.74\pos(1138.667,488.666)}头儿！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.36,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz23.29\pos(1234.666,728.667)}老爹指定新田为接班人了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请您不要胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:43.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止是以头儿接任组长为前提来协助整合组内的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要为了讨雏高兴 就说一些会让组里变成一团糟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:53.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要拜托给头儿就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了啊 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我过于草率地把短信发出去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.51,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz22.71\pos(1256.533,319.6)}回复
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.51,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz23.23\pos(1371.733,429.999)}喂你他妈到底是怎么回事！\N到底发生什么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「我为了尽快联系去了厕所」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「那之后的对话都没听到」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这样办了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 到底怎么回事啊头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根据跟班所说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:17.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像是利用自己的小孩取得了老爹的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟老爹就像宠孙女一样宠她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你这家伙在冷静地分析什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那混蛋瞒着我们把继承人身份抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连屁丁点仁义都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是现在应该马上去打爆的第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我冷静？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:37.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了挺有趣的话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:42.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在十年前内斗的时候可是一脸温和的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:47.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对那种叛徒 账必须要好好算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用他的命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么情况啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你所描绘的美好蓝图已经破灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会让你活着静静地沉到海底的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:13.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊跟班 他们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想说话的话 就先举手取得同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可我已经变成凝固的混凝土块了啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也直接跟他说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有想说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 哥 哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好脏！哥是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你要先取得同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:38.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:45.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 我听说你利用小孩子教唆老爹打算成为下一任组长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然因为雏的错老爹说了些胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有好好奉劝老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让他把继承人传给头儿你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:15:00.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明 为了组织那么拼命地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真难看啊 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也堕入肮脏的邪道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也把坏人做到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点对不起老爹你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们要跟这家伙算账
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:25.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等他沉下去之后 就拜托您再指明一次继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你们说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是顺势开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他就对我大声发火 让我别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟新田说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂跟班 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我听了要让大哥当继承人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想着要快点联系你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹 你说的都是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:06.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还刚夸过他「真的是确实为组内着想啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:14.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:15.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要接我的班当头儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,膳场 虽然你是头儿辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过让新田先当着没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊 一口气升到头儿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那我们来打个头儿call吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是值得庆祝的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:39.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:45.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿 头儿 头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:50.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿 头儿 头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:56.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿 头儿 头儿……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 快点先把我搞出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田出人头地啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:06.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,出人头地？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:10.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\pos(1034.667,845.333)}自从新田的个人派对之后虽然有些尴尬 但发生各种事后和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像鰤鱼长大了一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：ハマチ和ブリ是鰤鱼的不同成长阶段的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田变得好吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你要不要给他庆祝一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田应该也会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好的嘛 升职庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田为人很重义气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉应该会送点什么做回礼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 诗子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他高兴 然后 回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是长得像新田的临时工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是长得像新田的临时工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是长得像新田的临时工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 能给我一杯马提尼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想给他庆祝不过怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我想帮人庆祝 应该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:50.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 根据为了什么 为了谁而庆祝情况会有所不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不写出相关内容 什么建议都没办法提呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去问问认识的人怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 恍然大悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是生日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:07.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话是希望收到装有自己照片的相框
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 你这品味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那相泽你又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话 就常理而言选花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 别用那种这人居然送花眼神的看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,庆祝的话当然就是酒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说还能有其他的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,美佳你天天喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都在庆祝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对于诞生于这世上这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要被招待吃自己喜欢的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候果然还是惊喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好吓他一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 庆祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得变得不明所以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也听听我的意见啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想弄得盛大一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:55.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:56.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就全部都做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:02.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天回来的时候要按对讲机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我要准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你这么说我就懂 那我不就是超能力者了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给你庆祝升职
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:14.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:15.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:22.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后只去买需要的东西就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}高桥相框店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:28.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}电子照片洗印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}生剥鬼酒屋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,未成年人不能买哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花买多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}相框 相片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}新田喜欢的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,空瓶子倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\frz17.71\pos(1023.334,804.666)}惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}海的恩惠 多田的盐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:02.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田喜欢的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}表扬雏的时候用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的食物只能是鲑鱼子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:22.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想给他太多 就摆几颗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到雏为我庆祝的这一天会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟之前有发生过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不向她道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她会不会喜欢哈密瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在进来 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:01.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 死掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是小学生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会误以为被欺负了然后哭出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 蜡烛和盐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鲑鱼子的…妖术？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像个木鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说雏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:22:00.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你升职头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
